{"blogid": "122417810", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "2", "writerCollect": "4", "writerComment": "2", "writerFan": "3", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "27", "writerName": "Falling_低熵体", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_122417810.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "258816", "writerRankWeekly": "329723", "writerThumb": "6", "writerVisitNum": "3533", "blog_read_count": "1466", "blog_time": "于 2022-01-10 19:46:38 发布", "blog_title": "PHP开启fileinfo扩展的方法", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-light\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"PHPfileinfo_0\"></a>PHP开启fileinfo扩展的方法</h1>\n<h2><a id=\"flieinfo_2\"></a>找到flieinfo的路径</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">find</span> / -name fileinfo\n</code></pre>\n<p>这里是我的目录 每个人的目录都不一样 需要根据情况来换成自己的目录 下面的步骤也是这样</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>/www/server/php/74/src/ext/fileinfo</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><a id=\"_12\"></a>进入目录</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /www/server/php/74/src/ext/fileinfo \n</code></pre>\n<h2><a id=\"phpize_18\"></a>执行phpize命令</h2>\n<p>这里也是根据自己情况替换掉<code>/www/server/php</code>,总之找到<code>bin/phpize</code>所在路径即可</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">/www/server/php/74/bin/phpize\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Configuring for:</p>\n<p>PHP Api Version: 20190902</p>\n<p>Zend Module Api No: 20190902</p>\n<p>Zend Extension Api No: 320190902</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><a id=\"configure_34\"></a>执行configure配置</h2>\n<p>根据自己情况找到<code>bin/php-config</code>的路径</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">./configure --with-php-config<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/www/server/php/74/bin/php-config\n</code></pre>\n<h2><a id=\"_42\"></a>编译安装</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">make</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">make</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2><a id=\"phpini_48\"></a>修改php.ini文件</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">'extension=fileinfo.so'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>/www/server/php/74/etc/php.ini \n</code></pre>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 1, "time": "2022-01-10 19:46:38", "summary": "开启扩展的方法找到的路径这里是我的目录每个人的目录都不一样需要根据情况来换成自己的目录下面的步骤也是这样进入目录执行命令这里也是根据自己情况替换掉总之找到所在路径即可执行配置根据自己情况找到的路径编译"}